title: Supreme Court to host high-stakes duel over energy rule
text:
12 Supreme Court to host high-stakes duel over energy rule 
EENews: The Supreme Court will hear oral arguments Wednesday over a federal rule requiring that electricity providers give financial incentives to customers who slash power use in times of high energy demand.
